== Exported interface ==
<dl>
  <dt>{@link refcore_syntax. `?Syn'}</dt>
  <dd>Generic syntactical queries and manipulations. This is the primary
  interface for transformations.</dd>

  <dt>{@link refcore_fileman. `?FileMan'}</dt>
  <dd>Manage file contents, add and remove complete files. Also handles
  complete processing of textual forms.</dd>

  <dt>{@link refcore_esg. `?ESG'}</dt>
  <dd>Semantical analyser.</dd>

  <dt>{@link refcore_preproc. `?PreProc'}</dt>
  <dd>Implement Erlang preprocessor rules.</dd>

  <dt>{@link refcore_graph. `?Graph'}</dt>
  <dd>Low-level graph manipulation.</dd>

</dl>

== Internal modules ==
<dl>
  <dt>{@link refcore_erl_nodes. `?Nodes'}</dt>
  <dd>Syntactic node type-based information.</dd>

  <dt>{@link refcore_anal. `?Anal'}</dt>
  <dd>Analyser module support.</dd>

  <dt>{@link refcore_nodesync. `?NodeSync'}</dt>
  <dd>Semantic node operation synchronisation for analyser modules.</dd>

  <dt>{@link refcore_funprop. `?FunProp'}</dt>
  <dd>Function property server (currently only handles side effects).</dd>
</dl>
